      *
     C           *IN90     DOUEQ*ON
      *
     C                     ADD  1         @@RRN
     C           @@RRN     CHAINSFL01                90
     C*
     C           *IN90     IFEQ *OFF
     C           S@OPT     ANDEQ'Y'
